酒店的室內設計由Leese Robertson Freeman Designers公司打造，中庭裡掛有一幅16層樓高的絲綢壁畫《大好河山》，這也是中國最大的室內絲綢壁畫。<ref name="Press Kit">{{cite web| url=http://www.shangri-la.com/uploadedFiles/Shangri-la_Hotels/Hong_Kong,_Island_Shangri-La/press-room/press-kit/ISL%20Press%20Kit,%20English%20_updated%2024%20April%202013_.pdf| title=Island Shangri-La, Hong Kong. Press Kit| author=| publisher=香格里拉酒店集團| date=| accessdate=2013-09-28| archive-date=2016-03-04| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304072103/http://www.shangri-la.com/uploadedFiles/Shangri-la_Hotels/Hong_Kong,_Island_Shangri-La/press-room/press-kit/ISL%20Press%20Kit,%20English%20_updated%2024%20April%202013_.pdf| dead-url=no}}</ref>壁畫由40位來自北京的藝術大師製作完成<ref name="Frommer">{{cite news|url= http://www.frommers.com/destinations/hongkong/H37224.html|title= Island Shangri-La Hong Kong Review|publisher= Frommer's|accessdate= 2013-08-12|archive-date= 2013-08-26|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130826060537/http://www.frommers.com/destinations/hongkong/H37224.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>，懸掛於酒店的41樓至56樓之間，客人可在搭乘酒店的玻璃觀光電梯時觀賞到它<ref name="BB">{{cite web | url=http://www.etravelblackboardasia.com/article/91520/hong-kongs-island-shangri-la-the-comfort-of-home | title=Hong Kong's Island Shangri-la: The Comfort Of Home | publisher=Travel Blackboard | date=2013-06-03 | accessdate=2013-08-12 | archive-date=2015-09-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924002807/http://www.etravelblackboardasia.com/article/91520/hong-kongs-island-shangri-la-the-comfort-of-home | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。酒店內部共使用了771展威尼斯大吊燈，所有地毯由太平地毯公司製造，該公司在中國與尼泊爾有多家獨立工廠，以出產手工編織的地毯。

酒店離[[香港公園|香港公園]]和纜車站近在咫尺，這意味著住客能在清晨到這個80000平方米的公園進行晨跑和乘坐纜車前往太平山。據前副總裁與總經理顧樂嘉的觀察，這也是酒店受到休閒遊客歡迎的原因之一<ref name="HotelMan"/>。

== 酒店特色 ==
