=== 藝術收藏 ===

《大好河山》是酒店最重要的藝術收藏品。這幅絲綢壁畫由250幅畫布組成，它的製作共動用了40個藝術家<ref name="WPC">{{cite web |url=http://www.worldpropertychannel.com/featured-columnists/great-destinations/hotel-art-collections-hotels-broadmoor-resort-island-shangri-la-james-hotel-four-seasons-mandarin-oriental-7139.php |title=Spotlight: Top 10 Hotel Art Collections |author=Steve WInston |publisher=World Property Channel |date=2013-07-26 |accessdate=2013-08-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814101039/http://www.worldpropertychannel.com/featured-columnists/great-destinations/hotel-art-collections-hotels-broadmoor-resort-island-shangri-la-james-hotel-four-seasons-mandarin-oriental-7139.php |archivedate=2013-08-14 }}</ref>，花費了六個月時間。酒店另收藏超過900件藝術品。

酒店的宴會廳舉行各類藝術拍賣活動，主辦者包括邦翰斯拍賣行等專注亞洲當代藝術的公司<ref name="AA">{{cite web | url=http://www.absolutearts.com/artsnews/2013/05/15/artspublish/2348918455.html | title=Bonhams Hong Kong Contemporary Asian Art Auction | publisher=Absolutearts.com | date=2013-05-15 | accessdate=2013-08-12 | archive-date=2020-08-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808125125/https://www.absolutearts.com/artsnews/2013/05/15/artspublish/2348918455.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。除此之外，酒店也被藝術企業家Dong Myeong Kim選中，舉辦他的“銀行藝術展會”。該展會於2013年5月23日至26日之間在酒店的41樓與42樓舉行，展出了100多位韓國新興藝術家的作品，這也是2013年香港藝術巴塞爾展的一部分<ref name="MyArt">{{cite web | url=http://www.myartguides.com/art-basel-hong-kong-2013/fairs/item/1027-bank-art-fair | title=Bank Art Fair | publisher=My Art Guides | accessdate=2013-08-12 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140224024158/http://www.myartguides.com/art-basel-hong-kong-2013/fairs/item/1027-bank-art-fair | archivedate=2014-02-24 }}</ref>。

=== 客房與套房 ===

酒店有523間面積為479平方英尺的標準客房，17間880平方英尺的行政套房<ref name="NP">{{cite web | url=http://life.nationalpost.com/2013/01/19/room-keys-island-shangri-la-hong-kong/ | title=Room Keys: Island Shangri-La, Hong Kong | author=Barry Hertz | publisher=National Post | date=2013-01-19 | accessdate=2013-08-12 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130629225809/http://life.nationalpost.com/2013/01/19/room-keys-island-shangri-la-hong-kong/ | archivedate=2013-06-29 }}</ref>，一套944平方英尺的海景套房，兩套1416平方英尺的特色套房以及一套2253平方英尺的總統套房。每間客房與套房均配有落地玻璃，分別望向維多利亞港或太平山。<ref name="NP"/>所有房間都使用酒店自有品牌的香水。該香水可單獨零售<ref name="BB"/>。

=== 餐廳 ===

酒店共有7間餐廳。高級餐廳包括榮獲[[米其林|米其林]]兩星的廣式餐廳夏宮與[[米其林|米其林]]一星法式餐廳珀翠。這兩家餐廳均在2021年《米其林香港與澳門指南》中榮獲了各自的殊榮。

* cafe TOO咖啡廳 - 自助餐
cafe TOO由日本公司Super Potato設計，於2001年10月開張<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hotel-online.com/News/PR2002_2nd/Jun02_ShangriLaConcepts.html|title=Shangri-La Hotels and Resorts to Unveil 11 New and Innovative Restaurants and Bars|author=Steve Shellum|publisher=''Hotel Asia Pacific''|date=June 2002|accessdate=2013-09-28|archive-date=2020-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918131835/https://www.hotel-online.com/News/PR2002_2nd/Jun02_ShangriLaConcepts.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.superpotato.jp/en/works/island-shangri-la-cafe|title=Island Shangri-La HONGKONG|author=|publisher=Super Potato|date=|accessdate=2013-09-28|archive-date=2020-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814052822/https://www.superpotato.jp/en/works/island-shangri-la-cafe|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。cafe Too旨在为自助餐注入全新理念，整个餐厅空间内设置了七个不同的“烹饪剧场”<ref name="Cafe Too">{{cite news|url= http://www.frommers.com/destinations/hongkong/D51901.html|title= café TOO Review|publisher= Frommer's|accessdate= 2013-08-12|archive-date= 2012-01-04|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120104160907/http://www.frommers.com/destinations/hongkong/D51901.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>，分別提供不同風格的菜餚。餐廳以這種方式解決了由食客排隊造成的擁擠現象。餐廳提供包括壽司海鮮、中式點心、意大利菜、泰國菜、印度菜與西式菜等各色佳餚。

* 高美食店 - 甜品店
高美食店自1992年開張起便由香格里拉酒店集團的區域糕點師高雅倫掌管<ref name=" ISL patis">{{cite news |url=http://www.shangri-la.com/hongkong/islandshangrila/dining/restaurants/island-gourmet/ |title=Classic & inviting selections |publisher=Island Shangri-La |accessdate=2013-08-12 |archive-date=2020-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806203544/http://www.shangri-la.com/hongkong/islandshangrila/dining/restaurants/island-gourmet/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>一直以來都被認為是業界領頭羊，出產全港頂尖的甜點。<ref name="Alain">{{cite news | url=http://hk.lifestyleasia.com/features/wine-and-dine/5-best-summer-desserts-in-hong-kong-2013 | title=5 Best Summer Desserts in Hong Kong | author=Wynna Wong | publisher=Lifestyle Asia | date=2013-07-19 | accessdate=2013-08-12 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131013104359/http://hk.lifestyleasia.com/features/wine-and-dine/5-best-summer-desserts-in-hong-kong-2013/ | archivedate=2013-10-13 }}</ref>，該甜品店曾榮獲“香港國際美食大獎”的銀獎以及“香港美食之最大賞”西式烹調組別的“最佳甜點”殊榮<ref name=" ISL patis"/>。

* 大堂酒廊 - 國際菜系
大堂酒廊座落於酒店六樓，賓客可從落地玻璃觀賞室外一棵130年樹齡的[[大榕樹|大榕樹]]，它的維護花費2400萬港幣<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.shangri-la.com/hongkong/islandshangrila/about/ |title=An iconic masterpiece soars above the heart of Hong Kong |publisher=Island Shangri-La |accessdate=2013-08-12 |archive-date=2021-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124030232/http://www.shangri-la.com/hongkong/islandshangrila/about/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。大堂酒廊是享用下午茶的好去處，酒店的爵士五重奏樂隊每晚都會獻上現場音樂表演<ref name=" ISL lobby lounge">{{cite news |url= http://www.shangri-la.com/hongkong/islandshangrila/dining/bars-lounges/lobby-lounge/ |title= Leisurely teas & sophisticated cocktails |publisher= Island Shangri-La |accessdate= 2013-08-12 |archive-date= 2021-01-22 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210122070408/http://www.shangri-la.com/hongkong/islandshangrila/dining/bars-lounges/lobby-lounge/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

* 龍蝦吧餐廳
龍蝦吧餐廳提供由李志明主廚製作的秘魯油甘魚和法式鱈魚等各色美食。酒店的菜色曾被媒體評論為“帶有噱頭的現代海鮮菜系，菜餚有紮實的經典美食功底，但又提供創意的現代特色”<ref name="Lobster">{{cite news | url=http://www.asia-bars.com/2012/09/lobster-bar-grill-splendid-seafood-dining-and-cocktails-at-the-island-shangri-la-hong-kong/ | title=LOBSTER BAR & GRILL- splendid seafood dining and cocktails at the Island Shangri La, Hong Kong | author=Martin Archer | publisher=Asia-Bars.com | date=2012-09-22 | accessdate=2013-08-12 | archive-date=2019-06-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629183218/https://www.asia-bars.com/2012/09/lobster-bar-grill-splendid-seafood-dining-and-cocktails-at-the-island-shangri-la-hong-kong/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

* 灘萬 - 日本料理
日本[[懷石料理|懷石料理]]專家灘萬成立於1830年的日本[[大阪市|大阪]]，以為皇室與國家領導人提供美食而聲名大噪<ref name="WSJ nadaman">{{cite news | url=http://blogs.wsj.com/scene/2012/01/31/foie-gras-in-a-tea-cup/ | title=Foie Gras in a Tea Cup | author=Robert Michael Poole | publisher=[[Wall_Street_Journal|Wall Street Journal]] | date=2012-01-31 | accessdate=2013-02-17 | archive-date=2019-06-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616140110/https://blogs.wsj.com/scene/2012/01/31/foie-gras-in-a-tea-cup/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。灘萬是東京[[香格里拉大酒店|香格里拉大酒店]]的代表性餐廳。港島香格里拉大酒店的灘萬位於酒店7樓，由來自日本[[鹿兒島市|鹿兒島市]]的主廚柳田健二掌勺<ref name="Kenji">{{cite news | url=http://www.womguide.com/meet-the-contributors/contributors_profile/kenji-yanagita | title=Meet: Kenji Yanagita | publisher=Word of Mouth | accessdate=2013-08-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130626170628/http://www.womguide.com/meet-the-contributors/contributors_profile/kenji-yanagita | archive-date=2013-06-26 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。柳田健二曾經掌管過日本首相與日本眾議院議員們的家庭餐飲。 2010年，在美國有線電視新聞國際網旅遊頻道CNN Travel的“2010香港最佳美食”榜單上，港島香格里拉大酒店與九龍香格里拉大酒店的兩家灘萬日本懷石料理餐廳被列為“最佳日式餐廳”<ref>{{cite news|title=Winners of Hong Kong Best Eats 2010: The best of the best of our selection of Hong Kong's most noteworthy dishes and restaurants|url=http://travel.cnn.com/hong-kong/eat/winners-hong-kong-best-eats-2010-432973|accessdate=6 December 2012|newspaper=CNN Travel|date=18 October 2010|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809090302/http://travel.cnn.com/hong-kong/eat/winners-hong-kong-best-eats-2010-432973/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

