* 珀翠餐廳 - 法餐
屢獲嘉獎的珀翠餐廳位於酒店的56樓，由主廚施博德領銜。施博德擅長製作傳統法國菜，而非融合菜<ref name="scmp">{{cite news | url=http://www.scmp.com/article/668481/frederic-chabbert | title=Frederic Chabbert | author=Vivian Chen | publisher=[[South_China_Morning_Post|South China Morning Post]] | date=2012-04-04 | accessdate=2013-08-12 | archive-date=2020-08-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805050334/https://www.scmp.com/article/668481/frederic-chabbert | dead-url=no }}</ref>，他曾與阿蘭·杜卡斯共事，效力於杜卡斯的米其林三星級餐廳路易十五<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.shangri-la.com/hongkong/islandshangrila/dining/restaurants/restaurant-petrus/meet-the-chef/ |title=Naturally passionate |publisher=Island Shangri-La |accessdate=2013-08-12 |archive-date=2019-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191203014106/http://www.shangri-la.com/hongkong/islandshangrila/dining/restaurants/restaurant-petrus/meet-the-chef/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。珀翠餐廳對客人的著裝要求極高，對沒有著外套到來的男性賓客，酒店會提供一件外套掛於他背後的椅背上<ref name="tatler">{{cite news | url=http://hk.dining.asiatatler.com/restaurants/petrus | title=Petrus | publisher=Tatler | accessdate=2013-08-12 | archive-date=2017-09-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911014332/http://hk.dining.asiatatler.com/restaurants/petrus | dead-url=no }}</ref>。餐廳使用來自法國供應商安妮·貝爾坦的有機蔬菜，酒單包含了超過1500個品牌的葡萄酒<ref name="tatler 3">{{cite news | url=http://www.fodors.com/world/asia/china/hong-kong/review-36827.html | title=Restaurant Pétrus Review | publisher=Fodor's | accessdate=2013-08-12 | archive-date=2014-02-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219101148/http://www.fodors.com/world/asia/china/hong-kong/review-36827.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。酒店通常都有一個豎琴師現場奏樂<ref name="tatler"/><ref name="tatler 3"/>。

* 夏宮 - 廣式餐廳
夏宮是一家米其林兩星級的廣式餐廳<ref name="Tiff Lam">{{cite news | url= http://travel.cnn.com/hong-kong/eat/hong-kong-restaurants-avoid-right-now-michelin-guides-newest-stars-complete-list-49219 | title= Hong Kong restaurants to avoid right now: Michelin guide's newest stars, the complete list | author= Tiffany Lam | publisher= [[CNN|CNN]] | date= 2009-12-01 | accessdate= 2013-08-12 | archive-date= 2019-06-24 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190624073510/http://travel.cnn.com/hong-kong/eat/hong-kong-restaurants-avoid-right-now-michelin-guides-newest-stars-complete-list-49219/ | dead-url= no }}</ref>，提供諸如無錫肉排煲、{{link-en|蟹肉粟米羹|Corn crab soup}}和脆皮燒腩仔等佳餚<ref name="Yahoo"/>，餐廳的​​北京烤鴨也極受讚譽<ref name="andy">{{cite news | url=http://www.andyhayler.com/restaurant/summer-palace | title=Summer Palace | author=Andy Hayler | publisher=Andy Hayler's Restaurant Guide | date=2009-02-01 | accessdate=2013-08-12 | archive-date=2020-09-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929170419/https://www.andyhayler.com/restaurant/summer-palace | dead-url=no }}</ref>。夏宮的主廚葉志祥使用從菜場裡購回的新鮮原料，菜式受到中國宮廷菜系的啟發。葉志祥曾經為知名的康奈爾大學酒店管理學院提供餐飲<ref name="scmp Ip">{{cite news | url=http://www.scmp.com/article/673376/ip-chi-cheung | title=Ip Chi Cheung | author=Vivian Chen | publisher=[[South_China_Morning_Post|South China Morning Post]] | date=2012-07-19 | accessdate=2013-08-12 | archive-date=2020-08-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805173545/https://www.scmp.com/article/673376/ip-chi-cheung | dead-url=no }}</ref>。 

